Roles and Responsibilities:
 Provide Magento 2 training (development, debugging, testing, tuning &amp; deployment) to development team (Primary)
 Design and develop high quality e-commerce websites on Magento 2.3.x platform
 Integrate highly customized third-party solutions using a range of commerce technologies

Job Requirements:
 1-2 years experience in designing and developing large scale Responsive E-commerce Web and Mobile app using Magento 2.x
 Knowledge of service workers implementation for PWA
 Must be able to work with minimum supervision
 Must have deep knowledge of Magento (2.x) platform
 Must have knowledge of Magento Extension (2.x) development
 Must have knowledge of Magento customisation (2.x) (Platform / Extension)
 Working knowledge on building Node or PHP based applications
 Knowledge of 3rd party integration (Payment Gateway, external system integration with Magento 2)
 Knowledge of E-Commerce business domain is a plus
 Experience with caching and scaling techniques
 Excellent development training skills
 Ability to adapt and pick up new technologies